verbose_text: Immunofluorescence staining revealed a similar effect of acoustic stimuli on CLU protein levels (XREF_FIG); the protein expression of CLU increased in the group exposed to an AAE during cell differentiation, indicating a potential role of CLU in the development and differentiation of NSCs exposed to acoustic stimuli.
evidence: CLU increased in the group exposed to an AAE during cell differentiation, indicating a potential role of CLU in the development and differentiation
